{"tid":1344737,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"義和團運動","createTime":"2019-07-22T00:21:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T01:02:53.000Z","uid":49136,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"519ad7b4be17a00711a82031e96fa3ff6a58b72d","tid":1344737,"uid":49136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T00:21:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e5UiNfF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe5UiNfF.png&h=f5b28248&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n義和團運動，是發生於1900年清朝末期，清朝甲午戰爭戰敗後，在西方列強劃分在華勢力範圍、華北農村頻繁發生教案、天災頻仍及宮廷權力爭鬥激化的情況下，黃河北岸農民與中國天主教教徒之間的武裝衝突。1900年春季直隸成千上萬習練義和拳並號稱「義和團」的農民動用私刑處死了大量中國基督宗教信徒與西方人士，並縱火燒毀了教堂和教徒房屋；同年6月，清朝中央政府允許義和團進駐北京。義和團又先於清軍進攻天津租界，最終俄國、德國、法國、美國、日本、奧匈帝國、義大利、英國八國組建遠征軍引發八國聯軍之役。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aab1cb2cd839edc213d86095361e216753260446","tid":1344737,"uid":49136,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T00:24:50.000Z","msg":"資料來源：<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/義和團運動\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E7%BE%A9%E5%92%8C%E5%9C%98%E9%81%8B%E5%8B%95&d=D9%2BIkncl4BF5lZ8wPV9kyNKNpY%2BoLPIqDl3on0Jjdx4%3D&h=59a1de49\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/義和團運動</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/既視感\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E6%97%A2%E8%A6%96%E6%84%9F&d=D9%2BIkncl4BF5lZ8wPV9kyNKNpY%2BoLPIqDl3on0Jjdx4%3D&h=861ea348\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/既視感</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/斯德哥爾摩症候群\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E6%96%AF%E5%BE%B7%E5%93%A5%E7%88%BE%E6%91%A9%E7%97%87%E5%80%99%E7%BE%A4&d=D9%2BIkncl4BF5lZ8wPV9kyNKNpY%2BoLPIqDl3on0Jjdx4%3D&h=f9f218a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/斯德哥爾摩症候群</a>"},{"pid":"bb92997dab9332b1af09b2d9491f372764109c4d","tid":1344737,"uid":123854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T00:42:26.000Z","msg":"以前讀書有個論調而家既黑社會就係當時義和團演變出黎"},{"pid":"718ce5dfa3dc4c4cc7499c5bf29508ac7afb4f19","tid":1344737,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T00:54:22.000Z","msg":"元朗班仆街咪係義和團<br />\n唔出現個班咪清兵囉"},{"pid":"b60020c3dd8d85023c8046927adb15e23a844901","tid":1344737,"uid":49136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"718ce5dfa3dc4c4cc7499c5bf29508ac7afb4f19","tid":1344737,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T00:54:22.000Z","msg":"元朗班仆街咪係義和團<br />\n唔出現個班咪清兵囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T00:59:45.000Z","msg":"人地愛國愛港愛人仔<br />\n打漢奸梗係不遺餘力喇"},{"pid":"c79ae51d84cb146de8c4ea27e6ff75f68601f1fb","tid":1344737,"uid":49136,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bb92997dab9332b1af09b2d9491f372764109c4d","tid":1344737,"uid":123854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T00:42:26.000Z","msg":"以前讀書有個論調而家既黑社會就係當時義和團演變出黎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:02:53.000Z","msg":"新<span style=\"color: red;\">義</span>安<br />\n和勝<span style=\"color: red;\">和</span><br />\n共青<span style=\"color: red;\">團</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}